Subject: drm/amdgpu: Fix cat debugfs amdgpu_regs_didt causes kernel null
 pointer
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: 2161e09cd05a50d80736fe397145340d2e8f6c05
